  | "窒" => Some("Arriving at (至) her friend's house, Marsha found Cecile CHOKING her husband. \"What are you doing?\" Marsha asked. \"If he CHEATS (チツ) on me one more time I'll blow a hole (穴) in his head!\" Cecile shouted.")
